# Emacs Commands

*File Management*

Open/Create new file: `C-x` `C-f`
Save Buffer: `C-x` `C-s`
Save All Buffers: `C-x` `s`
Kill Buffer: `C-x` `k` (closes file)

*Navigation*

Select Other Window: `C-x` `o` 
Close current window: `C-x` `0`
Split window side-by-side: `C-x` `3`
Delete (close) a window: `C-x` `0`
Delete other windows: `C-x` `1`

*Buffers*

Show all buffers: `C-x` `C-b`
Select another buffer: `C-x` `b`
